{"body": "The amount of a person\u2019s appropriate maximum housing benefit in any week shall be 100 per cent. of his eligible rent calculated on a weekly basis in accordance with regulations 61 and 62 (calculation of weekly amounts and rent free periods) less any deductions in respect of non-dependants which fall to be made under regulation 55 (non-dependant deductions).", "citation_label": "UKSI 2006/214 reg. 50", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2006/214/50", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-04-06", "heading": "Regulation 50", "id": "b64319a8-da45-5c67-95c2-d2d2c4fb0429", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "214", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "50", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2006"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2006/214 reg. 50", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": [], "references_to": ["uksi/2006/214"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 50, "source_as_of": "2026-07-05", "source_document_id": "uksi/2006/214", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2006/214/regulation/50", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-05-uk-housing-benefit-entitlement/uksi/2006/214/regulation-50.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2006/214/regulation/50", "version": "2026-07-05-uk-housing-benefit-entitlement"}
